---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Hakkımızda - Voltz Power Tools | Marka Hikayesi ve Misyonumuz"
  description="Voltz Power Tools'un marka hikayesi, misyonu ve vizyonu. Profesyonel el aletlerinde kalite, güvenlik ve performansın adresi."
  keywords="hakkımızda voltz, voltz power tools hikaye, akülü alet üreticisi, profesyonel el aletleri, brushless motor üretici"
>

  <!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-hero-inner">
        <span class="section-tag">HAKKIMIZDA</span>
        <h1>GÜCÜN ARKASINDAKI<br><span class="text-green">HİKAYE</span></h1>
        <p class="page-hero-desc">Profesyonel el aletlerinde kalite, güvenlik ve performansı bir arada sunan Voltz Power Tools'u yakından tanıyın.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-diagonal"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission Section -->
  <section class="mission-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="mission-grid">
        <div class="mission-text">
          <span class="section-tag">MİSYONUMUZ</span>
          <h2>PROFESYONELLERİN GÜVENDİĞİ <span class="text-green">GÜÇ</span></h2>
          <p>Voltz Power Tools olarak, profesyonellerin en zorlu projelerinde güvenebilecekleri, yenilikçi ve dayanıklı el aletleri üretmek amacıyla yola çıktık.</p>
          <p>Her ürünümüzde en son teknolojiyi kullanarak, kullanıcılarımızın işlerini kolaylaştıracak ve verimliliklerini artıracak çözümler sunuyoruz. Brushless motor teknolojisi ve V-PACK batarya sistemiyle sektörde fark yaratıyoruz.</p>
          <div class="mission-stats">
            <div class="mini-stat">
              <span class="mini-stat-number">2020</span>
              <span class="mini-stat-label">KURULUŞ YILI</span>
            </div>
            <div class="mini-stat">
              <span class="mini-stat-number">13+</span>
              <span class="mini-stat-label">ÜRÜN ÇEŞİDİ</span>
            </div>
            <div class="mini-stat">
              <span class="mini-stat-number">81</span>
              <span class="mini-stat-label">İL DAĞITIM</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mission-image">
          <img src="/voltzgorseller/01.png" alt="Voltz Power Tools Atölye" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values Section -->
  <section class="values-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="values-header">
        <span class="section-tag">DEĞERLERİMİZ</span>
        <h2>BİZİ BİZ YAPAN <span class="text-green">İLKELER</span></h2>
        <p class="values-subtitle">Her ürünümüzde ve hizmetimizde bu değerleri yaşatıyoruz.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>GÜVENLİK</h3>
          <p>Kullanıcı güvenliği, her şeyin önünde gelir. Tüm ürünlerimiz uluslararası güvenlik standartlarına uygun olarak tasarlanır ve test edilir.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>KALİTE</h3>
          <p>Premium malzemeler ve ileri üretim teknolojileri ile her ürünümüz sektörün en yüksek kalite standartlarını karşılar.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>PERFORMANS</h3>
          <p>Brushless motor teknolojisi ve akıllı güç yönetimi ile rakipsiz performans. Daha güçlü, daha verimli, daha dayanıklı.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>GÜVENİLİRLİK</h3>
          <p>Her koşulda, her projede tutarlı ve güvenilir performans. Profesyonellerin bize güvenmesinin en büyük sebebi budur.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="footer-grid">
        <div class="footer-brand"><img src="/img/logo/voltz-symbol-green.png" alt="Voltz" class="footer-logo"><p>Profesyonel el aletlerinde güvenin adresi.</p></div>
        <div class="footer-links"><h4>Sayfalar</h4><a href="/">Anasayfa</a><a href="/about">Hakkımızda</a><a href="/products">Ürünlerimiz</a><a href="/contact">İletişim</a></div>
        <div class="footer-links"><h4>Ürünler</h4><a href="/products">Matkaplar</a><a href="/products">Tornavidalar</a><a href="/products">Taşlama</a><a href="/v-pack">V-PACK</a></div>
        <div class="footer-contact-col"><h4>İletişim</h4><p>Teknoloji Caddesi No: 123<br>Sanayi Mahallesi, İstanbul</p><a href="mailto:info@voltzpowertools.com">info@voltzpowertools.com</a><a href="tel:+902123456789">+90 212 345 67 89</a></div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-bottom"><p>&copy; 2025 Voltz Power Tools.</p><div class="footer-social"><a href="#">LI</a><a href="#">IG</a></div></div>
    </div>
  </footer>

</Layout>

<style>
  .text-green { color: var(--green); }

  .section-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    background: rgba(107, 224, 63, 0.1);
    color: var(--green);
    font-family: 'GeneralSans-Bold', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(107, 224, 63, 0.2);
  }

  /* ========== PAGE HERO ========== */
  .page-hero {
    padding: 100px 0 120px;
    background: var(--darker, #111);
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .page-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: repeating-linear-gradient(
      90deg,
      transparent,
      transparent 80px,
      rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 80px,
      rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 81px
    );
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-diagonal {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 60px;
    background: var(--white, #fff);
    clip-path: polygon(0 100%, 100% 0, 100% 100%);
  }

  .page-hero-inner {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .page-hero .section-tag {
    background: rgba(107, 224, 63, 0.15);
    border-color: rgba(107, 224, 63, 0.3);
  }

  .page-hero h1 {
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .page-hero-desc {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* ========== MISSION SECTION ========== */
  .mission-section {
    padding: 100px 0;
    background: var(--white);
  }

  .mission-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 72px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .mission-text h2 {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .mission-text p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .mission-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 40px;
    margin-top: 40px;
    padding-top: 32px;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--border);
  }

  .mini-stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .mini-stat-number {
    font-family: 'GeneralSans-Bold', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 32px;
    color: var(--green);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .mini-stat-label {
    font-family: 'GeneralSans-Bold', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .mission-image {
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    position: relative;
  }

  .mission-image::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    right: 0;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: var(--green);
    clip-path: polygon(100% 0, 100% 100%, 0 100%);
  }

  .mission-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  /* ========== VALUES SECTION ========== */
  .values-section {
    padding: 100px 0;
    background: var(--gray-100);
  }

  .values-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }

  .values-header h2 {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .values-subtitle {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--gray-500);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .value-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 36px 28px;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    position: relative;
  }

  .value-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 4px;
    height: 0;
    background: var(--green);
    transition: height 0.3s ease;
  }

  .value-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    border-color: var(--green);
  }

  .value-card:hover::before {
    height: 100%;
  }

  .value-icon {
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    background: rgba(107, 224, 63, 0.1);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--green);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    font-size: 16px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .value-card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--gray-500);
  }

  /* ========== CTA BAND ========== */
  .cta-band {
    padding: 0;
    background: var(--green);
  }

  .cta-band-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 40px;
    padding: 64px 0;
  }

  .cta-band-text h2 {
    color: var(--dark);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 32px);
  }

  .cta-band-text p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(26, 26, 26, 0.7);
  }

  .btn-angular {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 16px 36px;
    background: var(--dark);
    color: var(--white);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: 'GeneralSans-Bold', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% calc(100% - 8px), calc(100% - 8px) 100%, 0 100%);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    white-space: nowrap;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .btn-angular:hover {
    background: var(--darker);
  }

  .btn-angular svg {
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .btn-angular:hover svg {
    transform: translateX(3px);
  }

  /* ========== FOOTER ========== */
  .site-footer { background: var(--darker, #111); padding: 64px 0 32px; color: #fff; }
  .footer-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1.5fr; gap: 48px; padding-bottom: 48px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
  .footer-logo { height: 48px; width: auto; display: block; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .footer-brand p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }
  .footer-links h4, .footer-contact-col h4 { font-family: 'GeneralSans-Bold', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: var(--green, #6BE03F); margin-bottom: 16px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .footer-links a, .footer-contact-col a { display: block; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; padding: 4px 0; transition: color 0.2s; }
  .footer-links a:hover, .footer-contact-col a:hover { color: var(--green, #6BE03F); }
  .footer-contact-col p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .footer-bottom { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding-top: 24px; }
  .footer-bottom p { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); }
  .footer-social { display: flex; gap: 8px; }
  .footer-social a { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 36px; height: 36px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s; }
  .footer-social a:hover { background: var(--green, #6BE03F); color: var(--dark, #1A1A1A); }

  /* ========== RESPONSIVE ========== */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .mission-grid { gap: 48px; }
    .values-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .mission-stats { gap: 32px; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-hero { padding: 64px 0 100px; }
    .page-hero-desc { font-size: 16px; }
    .mission-section, .values-section { padding: 64px 0; }
    .mission-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    .mission-image { order: -1; }
    .mission-stats { justify-content: space-between; }
    .values-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 16px; }
    .value-card { display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: flex-start; padding: 24px; }
    .value-icon { flex-shrink: 0; margin-bottom: 0; }
    .cta-band-inner { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; padding: 48px 0; }
    .btn-angular { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }
    .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; text-align: center; gap: 32px; }
    .footer-bottom { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; text-align: center; }
    .footer-social { justify-content: center; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .mission-stats { flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }
    .mini-stat { flex-direction: row; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
    .mini-stat-number { font-size: 24px; }
  }
</style>
